computers.title: Asus ZenBook Flip S
computers.description: The distinctive ZenBook Flip S13 combines elegant sophistication with an all-new design that makes it more desirable than ever. Its sleek slim-bezel NanoEdge touchscreen and 360° ErgoLift hinge make ZenBook Flip S13 ultra-compact and ultra-versatile, and the 11th Generation Intel® Core™ processor and Intel® Iris® Xe graphics deliver effortless performance for on-the-go productivity and creativity. ZenBook Flip S13 brings you flexibility and performance — with a touch of luxury.

computers.title: Samsung Notebook 9
computers.description: While it may not have the best keyboard in the world, the Samsung Notebook 9 is still one of the best laptops you can buy in 2018. Packed with more horsepower than some MacBook Pros,but at a much lower price, Samsung has crafted a laptop that has just as much substance as it does style. Plus, on top of its killer specs, it’s lightweight and thin, making this one of the most portable 15-inch laptops you can buy today.
